						               													<description>This is a dual-use box, with loads of exciting content for both Conan and Mythic Battles: Pantheon players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Originally, way back in the mists of time, Corinthia was planned as a purely Conan expansion. Although the Conan game has a mountain of models, there were two specific things that some people (including us) felt we missed out. The first of these was villager models. Some Conan scenarios include villagers, and we provided tokens for them which work fine. But with all the other great models in the game, we thought that it would be even better if we could replace them with actual miniatures. So this is what we&amp;rsquo;ve done.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The other missing miniature was the winged ape. This has become something of a celebrity in its absence, as well as a bit of a running gag.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
